	tanding Room only IMPORTANT: WHITE OAK MUSIC HALL IS A CASHLESS VENUE. Ple
	ase be sure to bring a debit or credit card. TICKET PACKAGE DESCRIPTIONS: 
	GA Tickets - Doors at 6PM. Your entry into Solistice Sessions -- Full acce
	ss to floor viewing area\, outside patio\, music\, and bars. Show up and i
	mmerse yourself in the energy from the first beat to the last. VIP Tickets
	 - Expedited Entry Line. Beat the crowd\, skip the line\, and settle into 
	an elevated viewing area with the best sightlines to the stage. Includes a
	ccess to 2nd floor mezzanine and a dedicated VIP bar all night long. Table
	s - Everything VIP\, elevated. All VIP amenities plus your own hightop or 
	stageside table\, a bottle package to start the party right\, and discount
